There are also blooms in Pasco County.
Medium concentrations have been reported in or at sea in Pinellas County during the last week, low to high concentrations in the sea off Hillsborough County, background concentration to high concentrations in Manatee County, background concentration to high concentrations in or in the sea off Sarasota County, background concentration to medium concentrations in Charlotte County, background concentration to high concentrations in or in the sea off Lee County.
Respiratory problems are still reported in Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee and Collier.
No respiratory problems have been reported in Northwest Florida in the past week.
